column5: Has anyone been out East lately. I think most of the fish flew through the last couple days. Might take the drive is worth it?
I think the Atlantic still has some fish in it....
Nope, just got back.... I caught'em ALL ! hahah who wants to come over for a fish fry !
Good question.  I've been toying with the idea of going out myself.
does anybody have the webpage showing the water flow levels in the rivers? this is a great tool to find out if the rivers will be fishable.
here is the page for water levels you can change it to whatever one you want water flow
